hadiths[12]{hadithnumber,text}:
5885,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Aswad ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se dam karne ke barey mein malum kiya to unhon-ne bataya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke aik ghar ke logon ko har zahreeley janwar ke dank se (shifa ke liye) dam karne ki ijazat ata farmai ."
5886,"Ibrahim ne Aswad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke aik ghar ke logon ko har zahreeley dank ke ilaaj ke liye dam karne ki ijazat di thi."
5887,"Ibrahim ne Aswad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke aik ghar ke logon ko har zahreeley dank ke ilaaj ke liye dam karne ki ijazat di thi."
5888,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba Zuhair-bin-Harab aur ibne-abi-Umar ne. alfaz ibne-abi-Umar ke hain. kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne abde-rabba-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Umra se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke jab kisi insan ko apne jism ke kisi hissey mein takleef hoti ya usey koi phodaa nikalta ya zakhm lagta to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni angusht (unglee) Mubarak se is tarah (kartey) farmatey : (ye bayan kartey huey) Sufiyan ne apni shahadat ki ungli zamin par lagai , phir usey uthaya : Allah ke naam ke sath hamari zamin ki mitti se ham mein se aik ke luaab dahan (munh ke thuk) ke sath hamarey rab ke ijazet se hamara bimar shifaayaab ho. ibne-Abi-Sheba ne hamara bimar shifaayaab ho ke alfaz aur Zuhair ne taake hamara bimar shifaayaab ho ke alfaz kahey."
5889,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba Zuhair-bin-Harab aur ibne-abi-Umar ne. alfaz ibne-abi-Umar ke hain. kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne abde-rabba-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Umra se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke jab kisi insan ko apne jism ke kisi hissey mein takleef hoti ya usey koi phodaa nikalta ya zakhm lagta to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni angusht (unglee) Mubarak se is tarah (kartey) farmatey : (ye bayan kartey huey) Sufiyan ne apni shahadat ki ungli zamin par lagai , phir usey uthaya : Allah ke naam ke sath hamari zamin ki mitti se ham mein se aik ke luaab dahan (munh ke thuk) ke sath hamarey rab ke ijazet se hamara bimar shifaayaab ho. ibne-Abi-Sheba ne hamara bimar shifaayaab ho ke alfaz aur Zuhair ne taake hamara bimar shifaayaab ho ke alfaz kahey."
5890,"Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne Misar se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Mabad bin Khalid ne ibne-Shaddad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein hukm detey they ke wo nazar bad se ( shifa ke liye dam kara lein."
5891,"Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne Misar se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Mabad bin Khalid ne ibne-Shaddad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein hukm detey they ke wo nazar bad se ( shifa ke liye dam kara lein."
5892,Ubaidullah bin Numer ne kaha : hamein Misar ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
5893,Ubaidullah bin Numer ne kaha : hamein Misar ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
5894,"Sufiyan ne Mabad bin Khalid se, unhon-ne Abdullaah-bin-Shaddaad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey hukm detey they ke main nazare-bad se dam kara lun ."
5895,"Sufiyan ne Mabad bin Khalid se, unhon-ne Abdullaah-bin-Shaddaad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey hukm detey they ke main nazare-bad se dam kara lun ."
5896,"abu khaisma ne Aasim ahwal se, unhon-ne Yusuf bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se dam jhaad ke barey mein riwayat bayan ki, kaha : zahreeley dank jild par nikalney waley daanon aur nazare-bad (ke awaariz) mein dam karaaney ki ijazat di gaee hai."
